  _NPCName: Howie
  _lines:
  - It flew off somewhere in front of me?
  - I think?
  - I can't recall what it looked like though friend, I'm sorry
  - I know you'll be able to find it
  - I doubt it went far
  - You can always come back to me for an extra clue just so you know!
  - I'll try to wrack my brain to see if I can give ya' anything else
